high_descs: turn left and approach the counter with the toaster
take the spatula
turn left, go forward until you are next to the sink, and then turn left again. Approach the counter in front of you
open the drawer and put the spatula inside. close the drawer
turn around and approach the sink
take the spatula from the sink
turn around and approach the counter in front of you.
open the drawer, put the spatula to the right of the other spatula, and close the drawer
Turn left and go to the end of the counter.
Take the spatula next to the toaster on the counter.
Turn left walk to the other end of the counter, turn left, walk across to the opposite counter.
Put the spatula in the second drawer from the left under the counter on the left of the drawer.
Turn around, go to the sink.
Take the spatula from the sink.
Turn around, go to the opposite counter.
Put the spatula in the second drawer from the left under the counter to the right of the other spatula.
anns.task_desc: Put two spatulas in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn left and head towards the counter.
Pick up the spatula in between the salt shaker and toaster on the counter.
Turn around and head towards the counter.
Open the drawer second to left, place the spatula inside, and close the drawer.
Turn around and head towards the sink.
Pick up the spatula inside the sink.
Turn around and head towards the counter.
Open the drawer second to left, place the spatula inside, and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place the two spatulas inside the kitchen drawer.
